		<h2>From Dream to Reality</h2>
		<p>
			In 2018, a handful of ambitious students with a shared passion for robotics and engineering 
			gathered around a simple idea: "What if we could build a boat that thinks for itself?" 
			After discovering the prestigious RobotX competition, they were captivated by the challengeâ€”and 
